    "created_at": "2013-08-09T01:00:26Z",
    "updated_at": "2013-08-09T01:05:58Z",
    "body": "I've implemented intrinsics + traits for overflow checked `add`, `sub` and `mul` operations in #8408.\n\nFor `div`, checking `x / 0` and `INT_MIN / -1` are already required to make the non-checked division avoid undefined behaviour, so the checked equivalent would just return an `Option` instead of failing. I've left that out for now.\n",
